# Vue 3 Rules

## Always
- `<script setup lang="ts">` — never Options API
- `defineProps<{}>()` with TypeScript generics
- Multi-word component names

## Composables
- `use` prefix + single concern
- Return reactive values (refs/computed)

## Never
- `v-for` and `v-if` on same element
- Direct Pinia state mutation outside actions
- `any` in TypeScript
